Name: Denos City: Complete Game
About the game: Final version of Denos City. Adult Visual Novel. The main character (MC) is a young man who recently moved to Denos City and there meets Richard Collins, a wealthy and prestigious lawyer. And he knows his family too. But nothing is as it seems, and you have to discover the mystery that involves MC's past. The game contains many animations, environmental effects and sound effects. Content: - 6.343 images. - 145 animations. The game includes a walkthrough so you don't miss any scene of the game.
